OL,3,CMan who used video game Fortnite to
OL,4,Cgroom children jailed
OL,6,FA man from Bristol who used the video
OL,7,Fgame Fortnite to groom children has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for five years.
OL,10,FKieran Francis, 22, of Fishponds Road,
OL,11,Fwho was found with more than 1,000
OL,12,Findecent images of children on his
OL,13,Fdevices, was sentenced at Bristol
OL,14,FCrown Court on 16 October.
OL,16,FArrested in April by Avon and Somerset
OL,17,FPolice, the 22-year-old was then
OL,18,Fbailed with conditions not to speak to
OL,19,Fany children while enquiries continued.
