OL,6,FIn that time, three other forces
OL,7,Frevealed that Francis used the popular
OL,8,Fchildren's game Fortnite to befriend
OL,9,Fand groom children. He was arrested
OL,10,Ffor these charges on 9 August 2025.
OL,12,FIn a victim impact statement, one of
OL,13,Fthe children's mothers says that her
OL,14,F"son's childhood has been stolen, his
OL,15,Ftrust shattered, and his safety ripped
OL,16,Faway."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
