OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1761405966
OL,3,CMan who used video game Fortnite to
OL,4,Cgroom children jailed
OL,6,F"He was groomed online by the
OL,7,Fdefendant - a predator who
OL,8,Fdeliberately targeted an innocent
OL,9,Fchild. This was not an accident. It
OL,10,Fwas calculated. It was cruel.
OL,12,F"My son was a happy, carefree boy who
OL,13,Ftrusted people. That boy is gone. This
OL,14,Fis not short-term harm. These are deep
OL,15,Fwounds which will shape his entire
OL,16,Flife. He has lost his carefree
OL,17,Fchildhood. That loss cannot be undone."
OL,19,FAnother victim's mother said Francis
OL,20,Fhas "cast a shadow" on 'so many other
OL,21,Fchildren's and families' lives.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
