OL,3,CMan who used video game Fortnite to
OL,4,Cgroom children jailed
OL,6,FShe said: " While my children were
OL,7,Fgrowing up, I always told them not to
OL,8,Fbe afraid of the dark and that
OL,9,Fmonsters weren't hiding in the shadows
OL,10,Fat night... I now realise I was right,
OL,11,Fmonsters don't hide in the shadows at
OL,12,Fnight, but I was wrong in saying they
OL,13,Fdidn't exist. They are, and he's
OL,14,Fbefore us now.
OL,16,F"They will always remember this. While
OL,17,Fwhat (he) did won't ever define them,
OL,18,F(he) has darkened their lives and (he)
OL,19,Fhas no right."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
