OL,3,CMan who used video game Fortnite to
OL,4,Cgroom children jailed
OL,6,FFrancis pleaded guilty to five
OL,7,Fdifferent charges: Two counts of
OL,8,Fcausing a child to look at an image of
OL,9,Fsexual activity, four counts of
OL,10,Finciting a child to engage in sexual
OL,11,Factivity, one count of attempting to
OL,12,Fmeet a child following grooming, three
OL,13,Fcounts of possessing indecent images,
OL,14,Fand one count of distributing indecent
OL,15,Fimages of children.
OL,17,FDetective Constable Natalie Norman
OL,18,Fsays "Francis committed repulsive
OL,19,Fcrimes" to take advantage of children
OL,20,Fwho wanted to 'enjoy playing video
OL,21,Fgames'.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
