OL,3,CMan who used video game Fortnite to
OL,4,Cgroom children jailed
OL,6,FShe added: "Francis befriended his
OL,7,Fvictims, requested images and videos
OL,8,Ffrom them for his own sexual
OL,9,Fgratification. He then went as far as
OL,10,Fto distribute these images to other
OL,11,Findividuals seeking the same
OL,12,Fdisgusting and heinous gratification
OL,13,Ffrom such images.
OL,15,F"I would like to commend the victims
OL,16,Ffor their bravery and resilience
OL,17,Fduring this investigation. I do not
OL,18,Fdoubt this has been an incredibly
OL,19,Ftraumatic time for them and their
OL,20,Ffamilies, and their support of our
OL,21,Fenquiries should be commended.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
