OL,6,F"All of the victims and their families
OL,7,Fhave been safeguarded and provided
OL,8,Fwith support from their home forces
OL,9,Fand I would like to thank them for
OL,10,Ftheir support.
OL,12,F"They have shown true courage and
OL,13,Fstrength throughout and we would not
OL,14,Fhave the result we have today, and
OL,15,Fsaved possibly other children from a
OL,16,Fsimilar fate, without them."
